# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for phake 0.2.0 (https://github.com/molovo/phake).
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
#  * James Dinsdale <hi@molovo.co> (version 0.2.0)
